  ],
  "remarks": "Paya Parto is an entity that researches stable isotope separation, a key parameter for centrifuges component production, as part of Iran’s nuclear programme. It has close ties to the Atomic Energy Organisation of Iran (AEOI), which runs Iran’s Nuclear programme and supervises individual projects. Paya Parto is therefore responsible for providing support for Iran’s proliferation-sensitive nuclear activities.",
